# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok north korea was roundly condemned friday for its decision to withdraw from the nuclear nonproliferation treaty and for its bellicose warnings of a new world war .
# ::alignments
(c / condemn-01
      :ARG1 (c2 / country
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "North"
                  :op2 "Korea"))
      :ARG2 (a / and
            :op1 (d / decide-01
                  :ARG0 c2
                  :ARG1 (w / withdraw-01
                        :ARG0 c2
                        :ARG1 c2
                        :ARG2 (t / treaty
                              :topic (p / proliferate-01
                                    :polarity -
                                    :ARG0 (n2 / nucleus)))))
            :op2 (w2 / warn-01
                  :ARG0 c2
                  :ARG1 (w3 / war
                        :mod (w4 / world)
                        :ARG1-of (n3 / new-01))
                  :manner (b / bellicose)))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday))
      :manner (r / round))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok more than ### snakes , lizards , frogs and other exotic animals died of cold after being left in sub-freezing temperatures at a paris airport , officials said .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (o / official)
      :ARG1 (d / die-01
            :ARG1 (m / more-than
                  :op1 (a / and
                        :op1 (s2 / snake)
                        :op2 (l / lizard)
                        :op3 (f / frog)
                        :op4 (a2 / animal
                              :mod (e / exotic)
                              :mod (o2 / other))))
            :ARG1-of (c / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (c2 / cold-01))
            :time (a3 / after
                  :op1 (l2 / leave-12
                        :ARG1 a
                        :ARG2 (t / temperature
                              :ARG1-of (f2 / freeze-01
                                    :degree (s3 / sub)))
                        :location (a4 / airport
                              :mod (p / paris))))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "United"
                              :op2 "States"))
                  :ARG2 (s2 / secretary
                        :topic (s3 / state))))
      :ARG1 (a / agree-01
            :ARG0 c
            :name (n3 / name
                  :op1 "Poland"))
      :ARG1 (j / join-in-05
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (r / research-01
                  :ARG0 c
                  :ARG1 (e / extract-01
                        :ARG0 c
                        :ARG1 (g / gas
                              :ARG1-of (n4 / natural-03))
                        :ARG2 (s4 / shale))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (s5 / saturday)))

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                  :manner (m / motion
                        :ARG1-of (s2 / slow-05))
                  :frequency (o / often
                        :degree (s3 / so))))
      :beneficiary (t / team
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Yankees")))

      :ARG1 (f / factory
            :mod (c / city

                        :op1 "Guilin")

                  :mod (s / scenic))
            :location (s2 / southwest
                  :part-of (p / province
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Guangxi"
                              :op2 "Zhuang")
                        :location (c2 / country
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "China"))))
            :mod (u / urban)
            :mod (a / all))
      :ARG2 (z / zone
            :ARG1-of (n4 / new-01)
            :mod (d / develop-02)))

# ::id 6 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok taiwan 's consumer prices in october fell #.## percent from a year earlier , mainly due to falls in fruit and vegetable prices , the directorate general of budget , accounting and statistics said tuesday .
# ::alignments

      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (g / government-organization
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Directorate"
                              :op2 "General"
                              :op3 "of"
                              :op4 "Budget"
                              :op5 "and"
                              :op6 "Accounting")
                        :op7 (s2 / statistics))
                  :ARG2 (d / director
                        :mod (g2 / general))))
      :ARG1 (f / fall-01
            :ARG1 (p2 / price-01
                  :ARG2 (p3 / person
                        :ARG0-of (c / consume-01)
                        :location (c2 / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Taiwan"))))
            :ARG2 (p4 / percentage-entity
                  :value "1/2")
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :month 10)
            :ARG1-of (c3 / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (f2 / fall-01
                        :ARG1 (a / and
                              :op1 (p5 / price-01
                                    :ARG2 (f3 / fruit))
                              :op2 (p6 / price-01
                                    :ARG2 (v / vegetable)))
                        :mod (m / main)))
            :time (d3 / date-entity
                  :month 11)))

# ::alignments

      :ARG1 (s / stock
            :mod (c2 / continent
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Australia")))
      :degree (l / little)
      :ARG1-of (c3 / cause-01
            :ARG0 (c4 / concern-01
                  :ARG0 (r / report-01
                        :ARG1 (e / earn-01)
                        :ARG1-of (d / due-03
                              :time (w / week
                                    :ARG1-of (c5 / come-01)))
                        :ARG1-of (s2 / strong-02
                              :polarity -
                              :ARG2-of (h / have-degree-91
                                    :ARG1 r
                                    :ARG3 (e2 / enough)
                                    :ARG6 (p / push-01
                                          :ARG0 r
                                          :ARG1 (p2 / price-01
                                                :ARG1 (s3 / share))
                                          :ARG2 (h2 / high-02
                                                :ARG1 p2))))))))
